      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Completed内部我这样设计：ContentCDN指向Done，StudentDB指向PartiallyDone。Done回到GradeSync，PartiallyDone回到ClassroomService。这样区分完全完成和部分完成？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Completed",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Done",
        "Education_StudentDB",
