      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "PartiallyDone的终点不对，应该回到ClassroomService而不是留在当前状态。另外InReview的Approve直接到ClassroomService，不是到Completed。",
      "elements_involved": [
